Global analysis of sensory data

Source: R/analyse-performance.R
analyse_performance.Rd

Perform global analysis on sensory table.

analyse_performance(.data)

Arguments

.data

a sensory table

Examples

data(sensochoc)
sensochoc %>%
  specify(
    sensory_method = "QDA",
    panelist = panelist,
    product = product,
    session = session,
    pres_order = rank,
    attribute = cocoa_a:granular
  ) %>%
  analyse_performance()
